title: Non-diabetic islets, rep1
characteristics_ch1: tissue: pancreatic islets | disease state: non-diabetic | age: 47 yrs | gender: male | bmi (kg/m2): 27.7
growth_protocol_ch1: Once isolated, human islets were cultured in M199 culture medium.
extract_protocol_ch1: RNeasy mini kit extraction of total RNA was performed according to the manufacturer's instructions.
label_protocol_ch1: Biotinylated cRNA were prepared according to the standard Affymetrix protocol from 100ng total RNA after two-cycle target labeling (GeneChip Expression Analysis Technical Manual, 2006, Affymetrix).
hyb_protocol: Following fragmentation, 15 ug of cRNA were hybridized for 16 hr at 45C on Affymetrix GeneChip HG U133A. GeneChips were washed and stained in the Affymetrix Fluidics Station 400.
scan_protocol: GeneChips were scanned using the Affymetrix GeneChip Scanner 3000.
description: Gene expression data from non-diabetic human islets.
data_processing: The data were analyzed with R/Bioconductor using affy, affyPLM for quality control, rma for normalization and limma for differential expression analysis.
